Revision history for perl module Selenium::UserAgent

0.11 2017-08-15
 - Disable tests :(
 - Fix chrome
 - Firefox still probably broken

0.10 2016-08-19
 - Assert minimum required version for List::Util

0.09 2016-06-05
 - Stop using Test::ParallelSubtest

0.08 2016-03-15
 - Add nexus9 as an option for emulation

0.07 2016-03-09
 - Use Chrome's mobileEmulation option to set device-width

0.06 2015-07-13
 - Add new device candidates with specific types
 - Deprecate almost all of the old device candidates
 - Tests: Add workaround for Firefox not getting smaller than 335px

0.05 2014-05-05
 - Stop excluding passing certificate error switch

0.04 2014-11-23
 - Rename module to Selenium::UserAgent. This is of course a breaking
   change.

0.01 2014-07-18
 - Initial commit. The module applies user agents and browser sizes to
   Chrome and Firefox through a remote webdriver.